title: Bug 7752 - Export multiple files with same file name under different directories to zip file fails.
description: When exporting multiple files with the same name under different directories to a zip file, it fails to properly store the files.
OB: The observed behavior is not provided.
EB: The zip file should be able to store files with the same name under different directories.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Launch WSWB.
2. Create two projects.
3. Under each project, create a new file with the same name (e.g., "foo.txt").
4. From the main menu, select File > Export and choose Zip File to export.
5. The issue occurs during the export process.
